9 AN ACT TO AMEND THE LAW CONCERNING THE DRIVER’S
10 INSTRUCTION MANUAL AND THE DRIVER’S LICENSE
11 EXAMINATION; TO REQUIRE THAT THE DRIVER’S INSTRUCTION
12 MANUAL AND THE DRIVER’S LICENSE EXAMINATION INCLUDE
13 INFORMATION ABOUT THE SAFE OPERATION OF A MOTOR
14 VEHICLE IN A HIGHWAY WORK ZONE; TO REQUIRE CERTAIN
15 INFORMATION TO BE INCLUDED IN THE DRIVER’S
16 INSTRUCTION MANUAL; TO REQUIRE CERTAIN QUESTIONS TO
17 BE INCLUDED ON THE DRIVER’S LICENSE EXAMINATION; AND
18 FOR OTHER PURPOSES.
