22 TO REQUIRE THAT THE DRIVER’S INSTRUCTION
23 MANUAL AND THE DRIVER’S LICENSE
24 EXAMINATION INCLUDE INFORMATION ABOUT
25 THE SAFE OPERATION OF A MOTOR VEHICLE IN
