28 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
29
30 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code § 27-16-706, concerning the topics on which
31 questions are required to be included in the written driver’s license test,
32 is amended to add an additional subdivision to read as follows:
33 (6) The safe operation of a motor vehicle in a highway work
34 zone.
35
36 SECTION 2. Arkansas Code § 27-18-108(5), concerning the required
